4.77/5  rDev +8.4%look: 4.75 | smell: 4.5 | taste: 5 | feel: 4.5 |  overall: 4.75Poured 11.2 oz bottle into snifter glass. 5.4% abv
Appearance- Pours a glowing honey yellow with high white head that hangs around the glass before receding.
Smell- Yeast, banana, clove
Taste- Fresh wheat base grain taste with hints of lemon. Picks up a bit midway into a more floral sweetness with a banana bread flavor. The banana notes hang around and rounds off the flavor profile with a clove/black pepper spice note.
Mouthfeel- Medium in body with active carbonation.
