S: Delicious sweet-smelling aroma that’s chock full of banana and clove.  Distinctively weiss-bier and well done.
T: Semi-sweet taste upfront that’s heavy on the bananas and a semi-sweet finish that leaves a very pleasant taste in the mouth.  Classic hefe; it doesn't get much better than this.
