5/5  rDev +13.6%look: 5 | smell: 5 | taste: 5 | feel: 5 |  overall: 512 oz bottle poured into a weizen glass. Gave it the old yeast swirl as well. 
L - bright golden yellow color with a yeasty haze. Standard Hefeweizen head,  white and fluffy. Some lacing down the side. 
S - banana notes, soft wheat, and yeast. Not too strong on the nose. Just soft German yeast and wheat. 
T - soft bread up front, banana in the middle, with a nice clean finish. Very soft all around but crisp also. Banana is the dominant taste. 
F - medium body. Kind of a soft, fluffy feel but easy to swish around. 
