a: ultra cloudy pale yellow with one and a half fingers of head. lots of tiny bubbles. this is a pretty beer
s: big bubblegum note up front, then it gets wheaty, malty, and bready. light spices, banana and citrus at the end
t: quick bubblegum up front, then citrus, bread, banana, and slight yeast and spices. all of these flavours linger in the mouth for a while. hints of herbal/earthy flavours too? extremely flavourful
m: the carbonation is a bit harsh once it hits your tongue but it does go down smoothly. medium mouthfeel and pretty creamy
