4.51/5  rDev +2.5%look: 4.25 | smell: 4.5 | taste: 4.5 | feel: 4.75 |  overall: 4.5I had to try this beer. First of all I highly enjoy Wheat Beers. Second I love German beers and third because of the great reviews I found on this website.
