M= Creamy, lively carbonation. Finish feel is long lasting and salivating. Nice.
O= I´ve been waiting to review this beer because it´s not particularly easy to get in my area. Just so happens it was the first beer I had in Germany, and the right one to have at that. This beer deserves to be as high as it is on the Fame list. 985 charactersharrymel, Jun 15, 2011
