4.33/5  rDev -1.6%look: 4.5 | smell: 4 | taste: 4.5 | feel: 4 |  overall: 4.5Sun Singer had one of these lurking in their cooler so, not to be stared down, I grabbed it for a semi-liquid lunch; good call!
