This is an excellent Hefeweizen, smooth, a bit bubbly, and chock full of flavor. Terrific, almost enough to get me out of my "heavy" kick on which I've focused on bocks, barleywines, and Belgian beers. I guess I'll have to wait until spring, but this was a great tide-over beer until then. 1,194 charactersGehrig, Nov 24, 2010
