This is definitely a good beer, but maybe one I don't sufficiently appreciate due to a style bias. Hefeweizens and witbiers with big banana and spice characters aren't really my thing. That being said, this is a rather enjoyable incarnation of the style, just maybe not the A+ beer some suggest it is, for me at least. 825 charactersgeryeb624, Sep 14, 2010
