S: Very complex, yeasty smells, spicy, banana, faint hint of wheat malts. No hops. 
T: Taste is of faint wheat malts, no hops and complex yeast flavors. Banana, banana, banana pops out and hangs in the mouth. Extremely light hop taste, fades very quickly to nothing. Absolutely delicious.
M: Thin, light, crisp. Everything that this style offers. Perfect carbonation. Slick in the mouth. Can't ask for much more in this one.
