1.76/5  rDev -60%look: 5 | smell: 1.5 | taste: 1.5 | feel: 2 |  overall: 1.5I had heard so much about Weihenstephaner that I bought the only style available that I could find in my area and that was the Hefe Weissbier kind. It was a mistake on my part as apparently I do not like this beer.
